dct_title_s: India and adjacent countries : quater inch / Surveyor General of India.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, hachures, layered tints, spot heights. Includes administrative index, index to  sheets. Title supplied by cataloguer. Shows province or state boundaries, trigonometrical station or point,roads, telegraph lines, canals, forts, deserted villages, temples "Printed at the Survey of India Offices." Set contains various editions, some provisional editions. Sheets lack uniform title. Each sheet has a number, and area covered  by states .
